</li>
<li>schoenbergs chrarts of regions (Schoenburg, 1969)
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-sec-38-2-2" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="sec-38-2-2"><span class="section-number-4">38.2.2</span> Explicit</h4>
